# Exclude bulky / dev-only / sensitive files from the Docker build context.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/web/dist
**/server/dist
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.production
**/*.log
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
data/
.claude/
docs/
README.md
DOCS.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
